<div style="font-family:Georgia, Georgia, serif; line-height:1.5em; margin-left:2em; margin-right:2em; padding: 0.5em 2em 2em 0.5em; text-align:justify;"><span style="font-size:2.5em; color:lightgrey; vertical-align:sub; font-weight:bold;">&#8220;</span>&#160;<span style="color:grey; font-size:1.2em; vertical-align:middle;">Adds a holographic sight. Used extensively by military forces, it increases accuracy and weight but is a step up from a red dot sight.</span>&#160;<span style="font-size:2.5em; color:lightgrey; vertical-align:sub; font-weight:bold;">&#8221;</span></div>
